<?xml version='1.0'?>
<page
	xmlns:xsi='http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance'
	xsi:noNamespaceSchemaLocation='urn:magento:framework:View/Layout/etc/page_configuration.xsd'
>
	<body>
<!-- 2020-09-16
1) «Broken reference: the 'sidebar.container' element cannot be added as child to 'sidebar.main',
because the latter doesn't exist»: https://github.com/dxmoto/site/issues/66
2) https://github.com/magento/data-migration-tool/issues/452#issuecomment-436822971
3) We can not fix it in the vendor/mage2pro/core/Theme/view/frontend/page_layout/1column.xml because of
https://github.com/mage2pro/core/blob/6.9.1/Theme/view/frontend/page_layout/1column.xml#L10-L17 -->
		<container name='sidebar.main'/>
		<referenceContainer name='sidebar.main' remove='true'/>
<!-- 2020-09-16
1) "Intermediate breadcrumbs are missing on frontend product pages in Magento 2.3.5": https://github.com/dxmoto/core/issues/8
2) https://magento.stackexchange.com/a/250676 -->
		<referenceBlock name='breadcrumbs' template='Magento_Theme::html/breadcrumbs.phtml' />
		<block class='Magento\Catalog\Block\Breadcrumbs'/>
	</body>
</page>